♪ I love you more ♪

22:19.041 --> 22:21.041
-You're back.
-Katter!

22:23.000 --> 22:25.375
I changed.

22:25.458 --> 22:27.625
Look at you.

22:33.416 --> 22:35.833
It's the best costume ever.

22:35.916 --> 22:37.500
The beautiful-est.

22:37.583 --> 22:42.916
-But you are still my bestest friends.
-And you're still our bestest friend.

22:43.000 --> 22:47.583
Our bestest butterfly friend
that used to be our caterpillar friend.

22:47.916 --> 22:49.416
It's back!

22:51.000 --> 22:52.375
My balloon!

22:53.250 --> 22:56.041
Whoa, it's changed.

22:56.125 --> 22:58.916
-It looks different.
-It's better.

22:59.875 --> 23:02.708
That's what growing does.
Makes us even better.

23:06.083 --> 23:08.958
Happy birthday, Katter!

